cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM

The paper involves the use of Deep Learning with a convolutional neural network algorithm to build a diagnostic model for lymphoma using digital pathology images. This falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the use of Deep Learning and neural networks falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves image retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM) as it deals with whole slide imaging and digital pathology images.
